title: LMS Guest House Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Juice bar, African
description: Seventh Day Adventist guest house that offers a buffet lunch which includes salad, sandwich, soup, and fresh juices. Dairy is used, so vegans should inquire. One could also get traditional Kenyan dishes in vegan options. A snack menu is available at other times during the day.
